{"title":"人吃土、土吃人  蒋管区民谣选之一","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":1,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人吃土、土吃人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋管区民谣选之一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（这些民谣，在蒋管区湖南省滨湖、特别是湘西一带流传着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈叭狗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟官走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官打屁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快张口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特务头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不讲理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好动手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口口声声说民主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我偏唱个主不民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿粮上税样样全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年租钱还不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界不太平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在家少出门；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三更查户口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祸从天上临。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人吃土，土吃人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种粮不是吃粮人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饿死百姓无人问。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说上边来了米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夫妻大小都欢喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受苦受难五个月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树皮草根没得吃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总署发一斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"县府扣三升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"区长镇长打六折，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保长甲长不给剩。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}